{"id": 1914, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在什么情况下一定会使用滤镜？", "description": "滤镜究竟是通向更美的道具，还是带有原罪的虚荣饰品，来说说你的滤镜使用状况。", "record_count": 9991, "comment_count": 40, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170918171539MRCfdlwLJ38xEpKs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-18T17:00:19Z", "questions": [{"id": 3001, "title": "你在什么情况下一定会使用滤镜？", "content": "你在什么情况下一定会使用滤镜？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 236371, "content": "自拍，不加滤镜没法看，修图前的我是个土狗", "image": "img/option/option/20170918171632HP0GZxwEbJNFS5QC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236372, "content": "发在ins/朋友圈/微博的照片，加个滤镜体现我的认真和艺术修养", "image": "img/option/option/201709181718019ktpDT18MGrKUvxP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236375, "content": "食物，为了显得令人垂涎欲滴，煞费苦心", "image": "img/option/option/20170918171927nu3W0dO67CtzPTGp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236378, "content": "宠物，不加滤镜不能充分展现萌的精华", "image": "img/option/option/20170918172346opTn0l8AZrGMImRD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236380, "content": "有时候截图/资料图也会加个黑白滤镜，以营造扫描效果", "image": "img/option/option/20170918172330aCmE8q2SzFgcxl0U.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236381, "content": "街头和生活中随手摄影创作，滤镜决定了我是不是大师级别", "image": "img/option/option/20170918172449lAVLbdr7zKTcM8f1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236382, "content": "风景照，旅游总希望能把最好的景色留下，不怎么好的话就加个滤镜", "image": "img/option/option/20170918172513GOyzrjRFxuTc1QkK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236374, "content": "和朋友的合影/集体照，阻绝黑照，留下美好回忆", "image": "img/option/option/20170918171839ByOi6L1VgfJnepm3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236376, "content": "聚会或者活动为别人拍照，加滤镜是作为摄影师的责任", "image": "img/option/option/20170918172056mh7wDEB8qX3lxz0u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236385, "content": "不用滤镜，保持真实性才是我毕生的追求，keep real", "image": "img/option/option/20170918172711rRDG7q56VOAcYp9j.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}